      <description>&lt;p&gt;Brookins Consulting is proud to announce the migration of&amp;nbsp;this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="http://projects.ez.no/bcsimplesubscription" target="_self"&gt;project's&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;source repositories to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://github.com/brookinsconsulting/bcsimplesubscription" target="_self"&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/brookinsconsulting/bcsimplesubscription" target="_self"&gt;https://github.com/brookinsconsulting/bcsimplesubscription&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The BC Simple Subscription extension remains a projects.ez.no project, only our preferred source control has changed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Feel free to checkout this extension or any of our other solutions available on projects.ez.ez.no and GitHub.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
