      <description>Hello Xavier,&#13;
&#13;
This solution is a direct result of very specific customer requests shared with the ecosystem.&#13;
&#13;
It is possible others needs may reflect the truth that this solution is far too simple to alone provide for all possible requirements. It is still possible that this extension can be improved to offer more flexible features to provide for the use cases you describe.&#13;
&#13;
There is also the recurringorders extension, which might offer a more flexible basis of such a solution as an alternative. http://projects.ez.no/recurringorders&#13;
&#13;
Thank you for your interest and support.&#13;
&#13;
Cheers,&#13;
Brookins  Consulting</description>
